      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI differences <10% and E/uval <1.96 for all three primary QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement).",
      "rationale": "All three QoIs met acceptance criteria: stiffness error 7.2% (E/uval=1.41), yield force error 5.8% (E/uval=1.12), force at 40 mm error 9.1% (E/uval=1.78). Validation uncertainty (uval) computed per ASME V&V 20 combining experimental standard uncertainty and model numerical uncertainty. Output comparison level 3 achieved."
    },
